1
00:00:44,960 --> 00:00:46,800
I heard it's a flying object.

2
00:00:47,720 --> 00:00:49,120
I haven't seen it either.

3
00:00:49,160 --> 00:00:50,890
I have been waiting for a month.

4
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:52,660
Yuanyuan breaks her promise.

5
00:00:52,960 --> 00:00:55,640
Rubik's cube, hot pot, airplane...

6
00:00:56,240 --> 00:00:57,840
They all come from Jingyuan.

7
00:00:59,280 --> 00:01:01,040
It seems that in this world, only Jingyuan

8
00:01:01,040 --> 00:01:02,170
knows these things.

9
00:01:03,080 --> 00:01:04,200
Why do I feel like

10
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:08,120
it's not just a simple matter of advanced project design?

11
00:01:09,960 --> 00:01:11,289
The toy isn't ready yet.

12
00:01:11,920 --> 00:01:12,780
Once it's done,

13
00:01:13,160 --> 00:01:15,020
I'll bring it for everyone to see.

14
00:01:15,120 --> 00:01:16,360
Okay.

15
00:01:16,360 --> 00:01:17,039
All right.

16
00:01:17,800 --> 00:01:19,520
All right, let's eat.

17
00:01:23,360 --> 00:01:26,560
Sir, since you entered the court to assist in governance,

18
00:01:26,680 --> 00:01:28,120
the court discipline has been greatly strengthened,

19
00:01:28,120 --> 00:01:29,480
and disaster relief has been fully implemented.

20
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:31,400
Your strategies are like a bright lamp

21
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:32,960
illuminating the dark night.

22
00:01:32,960 --> 00:01:34,720
I offer you a toast.

23
00:01:35,240 --> 00:01:36,520
I don't deserve this.

24
00:01:36,880 --> 00:01:39,560
Assisting Your Majesty is my duty.

25
00:01:40,520 --> 00:01:41,479
From now on,

26
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:44,000
Mr. Shen will spend

27
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:45,600
many, many New Years with us.

28
00:01:45,640 --> 00:01:47,640
We can go release lanterns together

29
00:01:48,039 --> 00:01:49,759
to light up many, many nights.

30
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:52,920
Ayan is right.

31
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:55,160
Then I also want to wish everyone...

32
00:01:55,680 --> 00:01:58,000
I wish everyone in the new year

33
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:59,400
good health

34
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:00,520
and all the best.

35
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:02,640
Where did you learn these words?

36
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:04,240
How come I've never heard them?

37
00:02:04,240 --> 00:02:05,080
I taught him.

38
00:02:06,960 --> 00:02:07,420
Cheers!

39
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:10,840
Happy New Year!

40
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:16,640
Jingyuan.

41
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:22,640
The heavenly king covers the earthly tiger.

42
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:25,970
What does that mean?

43
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:28,760
Stop pretending.

44
00:03:30,040 --> 00:03:31,900
Those in the young prince's room,

45
00:03:32,480 --> 00:03:33,480
the modern models

46
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:37,160
and modern toys were all designed by you, right?

47
00:03:37,760 --> 00:03:40,090
You are from the modern world, aren't you?

48
00:03:41,320 --> 00:03:43,720
You're also a participant in this project?

49
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:48,970
I can't believe they charged twice for the same project.

50
00:03:49,079 --> 00:03:52,600
So your main quest is

51
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:54,800
to protect the young prince

52
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:56,760
and stay by his side.

53
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:59,360
And as a eunuch,

54
00:03:59,640 --> 00:04:01,800
you can be inseparable from him.

55
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:04,040
I suppose so.

56
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:06,420
I protect the young prince

57
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:09,160
to bring down Si Xinglan

58
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:12,160
and ensure long-term peace in Donglin.

59
00:04:12,160 --> 00:04:13,220
Speaking of which,

60
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:16,480
our goals are the same.

61
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:19,720
Then we are allies now.

62
00:04:39,880 --> 00:04:42,240
This is for you.

63
00:04:43,080 --> 00:04:44,159
What is this?

64
00:04:48,159 --> 00:04:50,560
The young prince bought this a few days ago.

65
00:04:50,840 --> 00:04:53,000
It's useless to me,

66
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:55,980
so I'm giving it to you.

67
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:57,720
Thank you, Jingyuan.

68
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:02,680
It's just a hairpin.

69
00:05:04,200 --> 00:05:05,730
Does it make you that happy?

70
00:05:07,760 --> 00:05:08,560
Men!

71
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:10,640
Prepare me

72
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:12,520
a whole box of hairpins.

73
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:14,980
I want the most beautiful and gorgeous ones.

74
00:05:15,080 --> 00:05:15,740
Go quickly!

75
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:29,280
Really?

76
00:05:33,080 --> 00:05:33,880
Your Majesty.

77
00:05:45,520 --> 00:05:46,850
What are you doing here?

78
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:49,240
What? Am I not allowed to be seen?

79
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:53,960
For an emperor to visit a maid's room,

80
00:05:53,960 --> 00:05:55,040
is quite rare.

81
00:05:56,760 --> 00:05:57,680
Move over.

82
00:06:05,880 --> 00:06:06,940
What's the matter?

83
00:06:10,640 --> 00:06:11,160
What?

84
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,760
Turn to the side a bit.

85
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:15,840
A little more.

86
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:20,800
Who gave you this?

87
00:06:21,080 --> 00:06:21,920
A friend.

88
00:06:23,640 --> 00:06:25,040
Terrible taste.

89
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:29,250
Your Majesty, if you can't speak nicely, you can shut up.

90
00:06:29,640 --> 00:06:30,840
The material is poor,

91
00:06:31,080 --> 00:06:32,680
and the pattern is ordinary.

92
00:06:32,960 --> 00:06:34,400
It doesn't suit you at all.

93
00:06:34,400 --> 00:06:34,659
You,

94
00:06:35,440 --> 00:06:37,240
why did you throw away my things?

95
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:40,560
I have plenty of them.

96
00:06:45,280 --> 00:06:47,000
Just wear what I give you from now on.

97
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:48,330
Gold ones, silver ones,

98
00:06:48,640 --> 00:06:49,600
with patterns, without patterns,

99
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:50,600
all kinds of them.

100
00:06:50,760 --> 00:06:52,600
I want to make you the most beautiful woman

101
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:53,800
in the entire palace.

102
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:05,080
Try it.

103
00:07:19,200 --> 00:07:21,200
You should also wear what I gave you.

104
00:07:24,080 --> 00:07:27,480
The experiencer's character goal is 75% complete.

105
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:33,440
The thing we raised

106
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:35,600
is almost ready.

107
00:07:36,080 --> 00:07:37,240
And before long,

108
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:40,520
General Song will soon return to the court.

109
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:42,640
Calculating the days,

110
00:07:45,200 --> 00:07:46,640
the illness should start.
